title: Aromatherapy — Cancer Rehab and Integrative Medicine
cleaned_text: We do not take insurance for our aromatherapy services. Please contact our aromatherapist directly for rates and availability. Our Certified Aromatherapist Catherine Winslow, BAAS, CA A Stage IV cancer survivor, Catherine brings life experience and personal insight to connect with her cancer survivor and thriver clients. She provides practical guidance, inviting them to explore and experience the wellness benefits of nature's gifts of pure therapeutic essential oils to support our body's own healing processes that have become overwhelmed. "Catherine has been an incredible part of my healing process and continues to teach me how aromatherapy can be such a vital process in assisting the body and mind. She is mindful, thoughtful and truly puts her heart and soul into her studies and works hard to perfect her craft to help others. What a blessing she has been for me and so many others." -Aromatherapy client
